{"title":"对话","authors":["魏巍"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":7,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"对话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"魏巍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国“侨民”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总统先生，亲爱的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你对侨民多关心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是遗憾得很！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你把我们丢到这儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却从来不问一问。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艾森豪威尔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对不起！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们仿佛见过面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可一时又不敢认。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请允许我问一声："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们到底是什么人？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国“侨民”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哎呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚刚分别了几年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您怎末就忘了我们？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是地地道道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道道地地的美国侨民！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艾森豪威尔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵哈，原来是老朋友！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我能否问你们侨居在哪里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活可还优裕安稳？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是否有共产主义的侵略，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"威胁你们的生存？美国“侨民”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说起这儿的生活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既优裕，又安稳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更没有什么共产主义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"威胁我们的生存。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是这里的国境严森森，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再不许我们回去见亲人！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艾森豪威尔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咦！这是什么国家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样骇人听闻？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要马上提出抗议，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要他们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把归国护照发给你们！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国“侨民”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说起这个国家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一派阴森森，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总统是大名鼎鼎的阎君。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不过他也说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是“自由世界”的一部分。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艾森豪威尔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哎呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原来你们是鬼，不是人！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来！快打鬼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们这些倒霉鬼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么要侵略我这老年人！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国“侨民”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不，不，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是和您一样的美国人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是在侵朝战争里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们才迁到这里当了侨民。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的，快来保护我们吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是地道的美国侨民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的，快给我们归国护照吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是最关心我们的人！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}